{"h22edf3c1g9535g4470ga639g917eb80044be": ["A fine talent with the drum. You'd do well on a slave ship.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "h70bec969gbc39g4e6dg97aag07393079286a": ["Word of warning: if you keep banging on war drums, you might just be drumming up war.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "hd5e50730g8f6ag4517ga7fegfe3f4db920ba": ["Makes me wanna dance.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "h8b24161dg84e9g4e24gac44gf841f3b266ee": ["O sing a song of Elturel, when foes are at her door.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "h46e69a45g6135g4a59g8c75gf4ef49eb95cf": ["Must you make us the centre of attention?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "he552eee7gc73ag49c1g92f6g5eae3a3bdeab": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "h045aa842gaa8fg4aa7g9503g807f369df7b2": ["That should alert a good few goblins to our presence. Not planning on discretion, then?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_Checkpoint_VB_CompanionReactionOnSong.html", "39059cb8-a42a-7d46-10c8-7c9859abd110"], "ha08fd06age96dg4bb6g882fg305c0543da77": ["Hells. Better a shrieking banshee than that racket.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\VBs\\GOB_